name: The Lone Ranger Rides Again

description: Amy Smootster is a high school social outcast who lives her life content in her own world. But it seems that Amy's world is full of strange happenings such as the spontaneous appearances of puddles of water around her and two-sided conversations with insects. Told with an arresting visual flair, we witness the coming of age of a special young girl who is clothed in awkwardness and oddities. With the help of her guidance counselor, Amy eventually accepts and embraces her abnormal abilities and discovers her place in the world.
name: Zero Girl

description: Panoramix accidentally breaks his golden sickle, and he needs a new one as quickly as possible. Asterix and Obelix decide to go buy one for him. But, as expected, it turns out to be quite difficult. The sickles cost more than they should, because of a few nasty criminals...
name: Asterix and the Golden Sickle

description: Cacofonix is kidnapped by Romans, because he is thought to be a great gladiator, to fight on Colisseum. Asterix and Obelix go to get him back, and wind up battling in the arena themselves!
name: Asterix the Gladiator

description: Julius Caesar has invaded Britain and succeeded, mainly because the British soldiers stop fighting every day to drink hot water (with a drop of milk), and refuse to fight over the weekend. Caesar, using his famous military genius decides to fight only when they stop to drink hot water and weekends. Asterix is asked to provide a magic potion for the British rebellion.
name: Asterix in Britain

description: A Soothsayer visits the Gauls while Getafix is away.
name: Asterix and the Soothsayer

description: A fakir from India ( Watziznehm) arrives at the village, in search of the "Gaulish madmen who can make it rain," in order to prevent the sacrifice of the Princess Orinjade to appease the gods.
name: Asterix and the Magic Carpet

description:
In the (probably) last Asterix and Obelix-album by Albert Uderzo, there isn`t a big adventure. In this one, Asterix and Obelix spend their birthday. Naturally, it`s not a traditional one at that...

Has reprinted material. None of it has been printed in the series before, though.
name: Asterix and Obelix's Birthday - The Golden Book
